555
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:33,151
These are the tea leaves I got from a merchant.

556
00:39:33,151 --> 00:39:34,777
I can see you are getting well.

557
00:39:34,777 --> 00:39:37,878
So, I am letting this master of tea review these teas.

558
00:39:37,878 --> 00:39:41,517
If there is something you like, the teahouse can get a supply of it.

559
00:39:41,517 --> 00:39:43,360
Much appreciated.

560
00:39:43,360 --> 00:39:45,158
Give them a try.

561
00:39:49,277 --> 00:39:52,255
I can tell you really love this job.

562
00:39:53,694 --> 00:39:55,459
