569
00:40:20,694 --> 00:40:23,987
General and Lady Rong Le are invited to his feast.

570
00:40:24,819 --> 00:40:26,915
Lady Xiang?

571
00:40:30,652 --> 00:40:34,942
I am Hen Xiang, from the House of Fragrance.

572
00:40:34,942 --> 00:40:38,368
